These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
House: wooden, townhouse, victorian
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, project-manager, nurse
City: boston, san-francisco, london
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, iced-tea
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the wooden house is between the project-manager and the nurse##2
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the townhouse house##1
5. the person traveling to london is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| House         | townhouse | wooden   | victorian   |
| Job   | project-manager     | lawyer | nurse |
| City   | london  | boston    | san-francisco      |
| Beverage     | milk     | mirinda      | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, water-polo, soccer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, november
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, siglo, aristoff
City: boston, prague, london
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the siglo-smoker##1
5. the person traveling to boston is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person who's sport is soccer is the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Sport          | water-polo  | ice-hockey     | soccer     |
| Birthday   | february     | november     | june      |
| Cigar   | aristoff  | siglo | tiparillo |
| City           | london | boston     | prague       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, reggae, country
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess, canasta
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, old-henry, montecristo
City: prague, liverpool, marseilles
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to prague is between the person playing canasta and the montecristo-smoker##2
3. the fan r&b is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is the fan reggae##1
5. the person traveling to prague is the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre          | r&b  | country     | reggae     |
| Game           | canasta | mah-jongg  | chess   |
| Cigar   | dunhill  | old-henry    | montecristo |
| City           | marseilles     | prague | liverpool |

