.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, sports, epic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, electronic, funk
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, pink, azure
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, french, brazilian
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the fan funk##1
3. the person watching epic movies is between the fan electronic and the person who likes blood-red##2
4. the person watching sports movies is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre    | martial-arts       | epic  | sports   |
| Music-Genre     | electronic    | funk  | trance |
| Color     | pink   | azure | blood-red        |
| Nationality   | brazilian | pakistani     | french      |

