2. the person who growstulip is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's birthday is in august##2
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Sport          | weightlifting    | rugby     | baseball      |
| Birthday         | october | march | august |
| Cigar   | tiparillo  | swisher       | ritmeester       |
| Flower           | begonia     | tulip       | daisy     |

