.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, adventure
3 different games are played: chess, whist, monopoly
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, subway, scooter
City: nizza, venice, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is the person playing chess##1
3. the person driving the subway is between the person watching musical movies and the person traveling to venice##2
4. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre          | musical | documentary | adventure    |
| Game         | whist | monopoly      | chess |
| Transport   | trike   | subway     | scooter        |
| City           | nizza      | edinburgh       | venice      |

