.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, egyptian, spanish
3 different pets are kept: goat, rat, dog
3 different games are played: bridge, go, monopoly
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the spanish and the person drinking soy-milk##2
3. the person playing go is on the right of the egyptian##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the dog and the person playing bridge##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Nationality          | spanish      | egyptian   | french |
| Pet         | goat | rat | dog |
| Game   | bridge      | monopoly | go   |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate         | fanta  | soy-milk       |

