.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
House: ranch-style, futuristic, tower
3 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, turtle
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, light-blue, mauve
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower, balloon-flower
1. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the person who likes ivory is between the owner of the rabbit and the tower house##2
5. the futuristic house is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| House      | ranch-style       | futuristic      | tower      |
| Pet         | rabbit    | turtle | lizard      |
| Color           | mauve | ivory     | light-blue |
| Flower   | sunflower     | balloon-flower          | tulip       |

