The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, september
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, art-deco
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, ritmeester, oliveros
1. the oliveros-smoker is between the gothic-revival house and the art-deco house##2
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fan techno##1
3. the fan salsa is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
5. the townhouse house is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | salsa      | techno | hip-hop     |
| Birthday          | march   | january      | september     |
| House   | art-deco  | townhouse      | gothic-revival |
| Cigar     | blend | oliveros        | ritmeester     |

