3 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, lizard
1. the colonial house is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the fan reggae is between the fan hip-hop and the townhouse house##2
3. the person playing poker is the wooden house##1
4. the person playing billiard is the fan techno##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
6. the owner of the cat is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
