.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, march
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, poker
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, dancer, nurse
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the dancer is in the middle##1
4. the dancer is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in december##2
5. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Pet      | rabbit     | guinea-pig | cat      |
| Birthday         | july  | march       | december |
| Game   | poker   | canasta         | mah-jongg     |
| Job   | librarian | dancer    | nurse     |

