3 different games are played: backgammon, domino, billiard
City: boston, prague, marseilles
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, white, green
1. the person eating lime is the person playing billiard##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes green##1
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating pear##1
5. the person eating lime is between the person playing domino and the person traveling to prague##2
6. the person traveling to boston is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Food      | nectarine | lime      | pear            |
| Game           | backgammon | billiard | domino |
| City   | prague     | marseilles        | boston         |
| Color   | white  | lilac    | green        |

