3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the fan house##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is the fan reggae##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
