3. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who likes grey##1
5. the person eating eggplant is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the chef is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
