2. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the mexican##1
3. the person eating kiwi is the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the chinese is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
6. the colombian is between the mexican and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality           | chinese   | colombian   | mexican |
| Food   | kiwi | zucchini   | pear     |
| Transport   | ship     | train      | boat    |
| Color           | fuchsia | lilac | purple    |

