3 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, whist
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, entrepreneur, doctor
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, zinnia
1. the person who growssunflower is the doctor##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the coach is between the person driving the tram and the person playing backgammon##2
4. the entrepreneur is the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who growsaconite is between the person driving the scooter and the entrepreneur##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Transport      | tram | trike     | scooter        |
| Game         | snooker   | whist | backgammon |
| Job   | entrepreneur        | coach       | doctor      |
| Flower           | zinnia           | aconite    | sunflower       |

