.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
City: nizza, liverpool, boston
House: victorian, ranch-style, craftsman
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, purple, white
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the ranch-style house is the person who likes amber##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes amber##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person traveling to boston##1
5. the craftsman house is between the person who likes white and the person drinking 7up##2
6. the person drinking milk is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| City        | liverpool      | nizza | boston |
| House         | ranch-style     | craftsman    | victorian        |
| Beverage       | 7up | milk   | hot-chocolate   |
| Color   | amber          | purple     | white       |

 